  "faccion": {
    "nombre": "The Alliance",
    "estilo_juego": "The Alliance combines versatile troops with precision weaponry and advanced vehicles, standing out for its flexibility and efficiency in any situation. It is a faction aimed at players looking for quality over quantity, capable of adapting to distance or close combat using specialized weapons. Their units are powerful and precise, but expensive and fewer in number.",
